////Muscles - Pathology - Muscle haematoma

Given	I'm logged-in with valid credentials
And	I'm on Page 08 - Soft tissue of Shoulder MRI
And I select the radio button 'Finding'
And I select 'Muscles' from the Finding dropdown

When I select 'Muscle haematoma' from Pathology dropdown menu
Then 'Add additionally pathology' button is enabled
And 'Intramuscular' checkbox is enabled
And 'Interfacial' checkbox is enabled
And 'Intermuscular' checkbox is enabled

And 'Signal behaviour T1w' slide bar is enabled
And 'Signal behaviour T2w' slide bar is enabled

And 'Hyperacute' radio button is enabled
And 'Acute' radio button is enabled
And 'Subacute' radio button is enabled
And 'Chronic, organized' radio button is enabled
